Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where school uniforms come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:04.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave the curry to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go visit Hanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny how they get pulled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I am going to be a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I will give her educational guidance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,How about a café?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And we can cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,We could do a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Or do fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,All boring ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You have some really amazing ideas, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, a cat café...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A cat café?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, a dog café is fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No, but I want it to be related to cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\NPresent your ideas with decorations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\Nmaterial acquisition and production,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\Nan ordering system if serving food, costume preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\Nwork shifts, and tear-down process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,work shifts, and tear-down process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, who has an idea to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry Tastes Better on the Second Day"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\NSo, we have a panel presentation composed of cell phone pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival" "Panel Presentation"\NAny others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to think of the whole layout, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,That's too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A curry shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! That sounds like a lot of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This only happens once a year.\NI want to do something cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Curry's easy to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry shop"\NCurry shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Will we have costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be a lot of work to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where school uniforms come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ordinary {\i0}curry made by high school girls in\Nuniforms with aprons? That's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Recently, there are many cheap-looking,\Nmediocre costumes. They are common.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ordinary uniforms! That's the\Neasiest and best way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's from the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! No way. I'm just mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? It's hard to make costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,If we're just wearing our uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I have an apron already.\NWait, is she in our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,She's small and doesn't have curves,\Nso she didn't look out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare. A daymare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,So, our class decided to do a curry shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea. A lot of people like curry,\Nand we can entice them with the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't resist the smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It must be stressful since\Nyou are class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama was eager to help out with\Ndecorations after I told her she's good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She's so easy to flatter, I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She likes to be in the limelight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What is your class doing, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We are going to do a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A haunted house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my first time. I wonder what it is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not very good with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you scared of ghosts and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not fair if you can't see or touch them.\NAnd you can't punch them if you need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I am going to be a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh good. You can punch those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If we use our desks as tables, we should use\Npaper placemats so they don't get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Tablecloths are hard to clean,\Nso disposable placemats are easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! You're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful there's somebody who will\Nstep up to take the lead during these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect people to be\Nso reluctant to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call you Leader Nishikawa from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,In exchange, leave the curry to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"Challenge Menu" "Pot of Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,"Challenge Menu" "Pot of Curry"\NThe extra large challenge just happens to be curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Curry is just a drink! I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's spicy! Way too spicy! It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, really? Somebody already finished\Nit yesterday, so I thought it was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Thanks, Mr. Stuffed."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Her nerves are probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't eat the curry,\Nbecause it's too spicy? What a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I can handle spicy foods. And that's because\NI'm an adult. I'm {\i1}older {\i0}than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this? It's way too spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:17.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What? That's weird.\NI'll have to rethink this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:22.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You couldn't finish, but since you're\Nboth regulars, I'll give you half off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?! This would be a waste,\Nso I'll take it to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultur--"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultur--"\NSo, I did lots of research yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I did lots of research yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You even took the pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,If I add a few things, I might be\Nable to tone down the spiciness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that curry's from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Curry tastes better on the second day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The cultural festival is still days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll use Mr. Stuffed's flavor as reference\Nand make it from spices like real curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't have a budget for it, and spices are\Nexpensive. Let's go with store-bought roux.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a cultural festival, so I guess\Nwe'll go with the ordinary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,People might think it's weird if\Nwe serve something authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Everybody will bring the cut\Ningredients they're in charge of,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,and we'll use disposable utensils. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:24.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I can make curry, but I'm a little nervous,\Nsince I haven't made large amounts at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ask Odagiri for tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Do these decorations look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ask Nishiyama about decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Preparing for the cultural\Nfestival usually seems tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,but those two have been unexpectedly\Nhelpful, so things are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to prepare to be a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:09:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. My classmates seem to know,\Nbut I am the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't you ask Tsuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsuji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...very popular among my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She does remind me of a small animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:21.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go visit Hanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you referring to her like a friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going. She's not there.\NShe's probably very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if you're doing something after school,\Nyou've got to see one of the seven wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that rule?!\NNo! I don't like scary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Because you can't eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I do like eating, {\i1}that's {\i0}not why!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is this Hanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You don't know?\NYou see, she haunts the bathroo--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Not listening! I'm not listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Are... they done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She looks super interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us go! Let us try to see\Nif we can meet this Hanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't! No way, it's dangerous!\NWhat if she drags you into the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I will give her educational guidance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, let us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--Okay, I'm going back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, w-wait.\N--Okay, I'm going back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Everybody's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,"Haunted House"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go back to the classroom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a high school girl ghost who's been\Nin second place for a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,and has unfinished business in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in charge of the curry, right?\NCome on and do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo is gone, too.\NWhere in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo went with Miss Yoko\Nto visit Hanako in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! The Hanako from the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the point of looking at {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,To give educational guidance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,They're up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,We have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph, it's impossible to look\Nin every toilet in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Oh yeah? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, you'll be a zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I am supposed to wear makeup and scare\Nthe visitors, but I still do not know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, I realized that there is\Na professional monster here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I move stealthily like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a human and move as I think a human would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No! You are not a zombie, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And you'll be scaring people?\NYou're not that kind of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Your classmates don't understand you at all!\NDoes your homeroom teacher know about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This must be what it means to be "monster parents,"\Nhuh? We're not your parents, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I am looking forward to the\Ncultural festival. I will be going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,As am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you both! Wait, you both come anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sonobe, I heard you snuck\Ninto Class 3! Get on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cultural Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We will now commence Central Girls'\NHigh School's 32nd cultural festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"Beautiful Metamorphosis"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"Beautiful Metamorphosis"\NThe theme is "Beautiful Metamorphosis."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's all do our best and make this\Na wonderful day full of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. The curry is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do our best, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, eating curry probably isn't\Nthe first thing people do--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Two bowls, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm... Actually, make that three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't have energy unless I eat.\NAnd it'll be good advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have your fortune told?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry" "First year, Class 3"\NHm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry" "First year, Class 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm! This is yummy! Plain delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:14:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What a simple and gentle flavor! It tastes like\Nhigh school girls made it. So ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NWelcome! We have curry made by high school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NThis curry is made by high school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NI see. It's plain delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, so many people are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,We can do better than this.\NI'll go out to advertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe Futaba can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wouldn't want her to eat all the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,A lot of people come to our\Ncultural festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NAll right! Let's attract some customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I think there's a place that's selling it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.27,Main,,0,0,0,,First year, Class 3's\Nhomemade curry is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's plain delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NIt's plain delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NIt's funny how they get pulled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NThey just keep getting pulled--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It already has a mosaic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:53.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Miss Yoko, you were trying\Nto draw in customers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a zombie. It's rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:16:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You put way too much into\Nthis for just a cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:03.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe helped me with the makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried out pastry shop techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You tried out pastry shop techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.47,Main,,0,0,0,,How long have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not know why, but whenever I go out\Nto advertise, people outright avoid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Commoners must shrink back in fear when\Nsomeone of Miss Yoko's rank speaks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm used to {\i1}him {\i0}popping up unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, do not fret about their reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's because of the zombie makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! They tremble with fear\Nbecause of your realistic acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, I get it. You should get your ears checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how is the haunted house going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It is surprisingly lively. I have not\Nbeen that involved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to go through the haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It's made by high schoolers,\Nso it's probably fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Maybe even I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:18.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mua ha, ha. You've entered, Futaba Odagiri.\NI'll scare you and avenge my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's darker than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Boo! Feel my vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I said, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,--Right here...\N--Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's here. It looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, no pushing. Please line up\Nso you don't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I ended up attracting customers here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.71,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fried Octopus Balls"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"Rockin' Popcorn"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,High school cultural festivals are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This cute cultural feel is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sonobe. Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,So forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, er, I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's just juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess if it's juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Apple" "Orange" "Grape" "Fruit" "Oolong Tea" "Cider"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Apple" "Orange" "Grape" "Fruit" "Oolong Tea" "Cider"\NLet's see, I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Apple" "Orange" "Grape" "Fruit" "Oolong Tea" "Cider"\NI recommend the vegetable juice for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,"Vegetable Juice"\NI recommend the vegetable juice for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You just look like someone who'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I give off that image?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go! Free extra large for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's about to spill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you going to see Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this to her, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of trial? But, even if I've\Ngone bad, I must do this as former maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And this is for Yoko and Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I will not fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NHey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.71,Main,,0,0,0,,"Curry"\NI'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Haunted houses and stuff are just\Nnot good. Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,The quality of Miss Yoko's\Ncostume was just way too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't come near me with that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Take that, Futaba Odagiri! I can't believe\Nyou're scared of a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Boo! I'm a ghost. Feel my vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. You're trying very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No! You're supposed to be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there... are the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...the remnants of what used to be a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait-- This is just vegetable juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke Battle"\N♪ Sakura! That's the name of an angel! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Sakura! That's the name of an angel! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to separate trash
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and dispose of it in the marked areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"--Festival"\Nand dispose of it in the marked areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Students who are done cleaning,\Nplease make your way home promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Phew. The cultural festival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Both the curry shop and haunted\Nhouse were a success. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Quite right. They will make great memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I was very anxious. I thought I would be\Nthe only one who could not be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,However, everybody did have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,When will you take that makeup off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I have it on already, so I\Nwill wait until I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! You should take it off. You'll get\Narrested. They'll be after your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is\Nso entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Money..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't say here"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We each have our own happiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's enjoy life as much as we want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's crazy and messy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's the rock scissors parade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the three of us gather{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For rock, paper, scissors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll tie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it'll never end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parade's started, and you have to join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer to one times three{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to know, then come here!{\i0}
